            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <del rend="erasure">[<expan><abbr>I</abbr><ex>ovi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>O</abbr><ex>ptimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>aximo</ex></expan></del>] <lb n="2"/>Iunoni Reginae <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan><lb break="no" n="3"/>nervae Doctrici <lb n="4"/>Marti et Victoriae <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Montan</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Celer <lb n="6"/>missus honesta <lb n="7"/>missione ex b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciario</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>quod <expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> susceperam <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="10"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edicata</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Id</abbr><ex>ibus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Dec</abbr><ex>embribus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> Seve<lb break="no" n="11"/>ro et <del rend="erasure">Albino <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>are</ex></expan></del> II co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sekundär verwendet im Fundament eines spätantiken Gebäudes. Z. 4: ET-Ligatur; Z. 7: B und F durch eine Horizontalhaste mittig ligiert, sicilicus über COS; Z. 8: EP-, ER-, AM-Ligaturen; Z. 8: blattförmige hederae als Worttrenner; Z. 9: E klein am Zeilenende. (B): Z. 1: [[I(ovi) O(ptimo) M(aximo)]]; Z. 2/3: Mi/nervae.</p>
            </div>
